**File:** calculate.ipd

**Shows:** Usage of Mapping Element, mappings, XPath functions

**Components:** Start Element, Mapping Element, End Element, Connection

A very simple process which calculates a sum from two numeric variables using an XPath function. It logs the result and provides it as an output of the process through a mapping in the End Element.
